## 📝 When to Update Each File

### Update Table

| File | When to Update | What to Update | Who |
|------|----------------|----------------|-----|
| **`docs/STATUS.md`** | After each slice completed | - Slice progress (✅/⚠️/❌)<br>- Metrics (tests pass rate, etc.)<br>- Next milestone | AI |
| **`docs/ai/LESSONS.md`** | After each task | - What worked<br>- What didn't work<br>- Rules for next time | AI |
| **`docs/api/[module]/README.md`** | When creating/changing endpoint | - Request/Response<br>- Usage examples<br>- Error codes | AI |
| **`docs/SEARCH.md`** | When adding new topic/feature | - Keywords mapped to files<br>- New topics | AI |
| **`specs/[project]/SPEC.md`** | When starting project or changing scope | - Objective<br>- Scope<br>- Timeline | Human |
| **`specs/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/slice.json`** | Before implementing (human) | - Objective<br>- Ticket<br>- Git metadata<br>- Files<br>- Acceptance<br>- Tests<br>- Documentation | Human |
| **`docs/CONTEXTO.md`** | When project context changes | - Target<br>- Business model<br>- Architecture | Human |
| **`docs/WORKFLOW.md`** | When improving process | - Implementation flow<br>- Available commands | Human |
| **`docs/ai/PRINCIPLES.md`** | Rarely (1x/month or less) | - Fundamental principles | Human |
| **`docs/ai/RULES.yaml`** | When there are new learnings | - Behavior rules<br>- Triggers | Human |

