| **Slice spec** | `specs/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/slice.json` | "files, acceptance, tests" |
| **Slice PR** | `specs/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/pr.md` o `specs-fix/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/pr.md` | "PR del slice" |
| **Slice git metadata** | `specs/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/slice.json -> ticket + git.*` | "rama declarada y base del worktree" |
| **API endpoint** | `docs/api/[module]/README.md` | "Request, Response, Examples" |
| **Keyword search** | `docs/SEARCH.md` | "auth → hooks/useAuth.ts" |
| **Master index** | `docs/INDEX.md` | Links to all files |
| **Workflow** | `docs/WORKFLOW.md` | "How to implement" |
| **PR por slice** | `specs/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/pr.md` | Cuerpo fuente del PR del slice |
| **Historical (analysis)** | `docs/archive/analysis/` | Old analysis |

