## ✅ Documentation Checklist per Slice

### Before Implementing (Human)

```markdown
## Slice Creation Checklist

- [ ] SPEC exists in `specs/[project]/SPEC.md`
- [ ] SLICE created in `specs/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/slice.json`
- [ ] `pr.md` creado en el mismo directorio del slice
- [ ] `ticket` cargado en el slice
- [ ] `git.branch_type`, `git.base_branch`, `git.branch_slug` y `git.branch_name` cargados
- [ ] SLICE has unique `slice_id`
- [ ] SLICE has descriptive `title`
- [ ] SLICE has clear `objective` (1-2 sentences)
- [ ] SLICE has `files` defined (file list)
- [ ] SLICE has `acceptance` criteria (measurable)
- [ ] SLICE has `tests` defined
- [ ] SLICE has `documentation` defined

### Example of Complete Slice

```json
{
  "slice_id": "slice-03-ingest",
  "ticket": "ABC-123",
  "title": "Core Ingest API",
  "objective": "Implement LLM request ingestion endpoint",
  "git": {
    "branch_type": "feature",
    "base_branch": "develop",
    "branch_slug": "core-ingest-api",
    "branch_name": "feature/ABC-123-core-ingest-api"
  },
  "files": [
    "app/api/v1/ingest/route.ts",
    "lib/ingest/validate.ts",
    "lib/ingest/service.ts"
  ],
  "acceptance": [
    "Endpoint accepts requests with valid API key",
    "Endpoint rejects requests without API key (401)",
    "Endpoint validates payload correctly",
    "Endpoint calculates costs automatically",
    "E2E tests pass"
  ],
  "tests": [
    "test/e2e/ingest.test.ts"
  ],
  "documentation": [
    "docs/api/v1/ingest/README.md"
  ]
}
```
```

---

### During Implementation (AI)

```markdown
## Implementation Checklist

- [ ] Read `docs/ai/PRINCIPLES.md`
- [ ] Read `docs/ai/RULES.yaml`
- [ ] Read `specs/[project]/slices/[slice-id]/slice.json`
- [ ] Bootstrap con `tools/scripts/start-slice.sh`
- [ ] Verified slice with `/verify-slice`
- [ ] Only touching files in `slice.files`
- [ ] Only implementing `slice.acceptance`
- [ ] Following principles and rules
```

---

### After Implementation (AI)

```markdown
## Closing Checklist

- [ ] Tests pass (`slice.tests`)
- [ ] Acceptance criteria met (`slice.acceptance`)
- [ ] Documentation updated (`slice.documentation`)
  - [ ] `docs/api/[module]/README.md` (if endpoint)
  - [ ] `docs/SEARCH.md` (if new topic)
- [ ] `docs/STATUS.md` updated
- [ ] `docs/ai/LESSONS.md` updated
- [ ] `pr.md` actualizado en el directorio del slice
- [ ] PR created with template from `GITFLOW_PR_GUIDE.md`
```

