## 🎯 Documentation Commands

### For Humans

| Command | Purpose | Example |
|---------|---------|---------|
| `/create-slice [project] [name]` | Create slice template | `/create-slice {{PROJECT_SLUG}} slice-04-dashboard` |
| `/verify-slice [project] [slice]` | Verify slice is complete | `/verify-slice {{PROJECT_SLUG}} slice-03-ingest` |
| `bash tools/scripts/start-slice.sh <slice.json>` | Crear rama + worktree del slice | `bash tools/scripts/start-slice.sh specs/{{PROJECT_SLUG}}/slices/slice-03-ingest/slice.json` |

### For AI

| Action | Automatic Trigger |
|--------|-------------------|
| Update `docs/STATUS.md` | `slice_completed: true` |
| Update `docs/ai/LESSONS.md` | `slice_completed: true` |
| Update `docs/api/[module]/README.md` | `api_endpoint_created: true` |
| Update `docs/SEARCH.md` | `new_keyword_discovered: true` |

