## 📊 Documentation Metrics

### Metrics to Track

```yaml
documentation_metrics:
  files_updated_per_slice: "Should be >= 2 (STATUS + LESSONS)"
  api_docs_coverage: "% of endpoints documented (should be 100%)"
  lessons_count: "Number of lessons learned (should grow)"
  search_keywords: "Number of mapped keywords (should grow)"
```

### Targets

| Metric | Target | When to Measure |
|--------|--------|-----------------|
| **Files updated per slice** | >= 2 | Per slice |
| **API docs coverage** | 100% | Per endpoint |
| **Lessons count** | 1+ per slice | Per slice |
| **Search keywords** | Growing | Weekly |

